For golfers, he said it’s best to adjust their exercise program with an eye toward "off-season improvements and in-season maintenance."

Both experts emphasized that individuals should [check with a physician](https://www.foxnews.com/category/health/health-care) before starting any exercise program and should consult a physical therapist for any ailments that may limit activities.

